Kanada, Mareykanka, Japan, Hindiya, Sri Lanka, Australia, Faransiiska, Argentina, Jarmalka iyo Thailand ayaa ka mid ahaa dadka ugu horeeya ee qorsheeyay inay ka soo qaadaan muwaadiniintooda.
