Rakaabka ayaa la baaray ka hor inta aan la duulin, afar qof oo reer Koonfur Afrika ah oo la ogaaday calaamadaha cudurka coronavirus ayaa lagu daayay Shiinaha si loo yareeyo halista.
Waxaa la soo daadgureeyay oo keliya dadka reer Koonfur Afrika ah ee baaritaanka cudurka faafa uu ahaa mid taban.
Dhammaan muwaadiniinta Koonfur Afrika, oo ay ku jiraan duulimaadyada duulimaadka, duuliyeyaasha, shaqaalaha hudheelka, booliska iyo askarta ka qayb galay howlgalka bani'aadamnimada, ayaa la sameeyay baaritaano, waxayna si taxaddar leh ula socdeen iyagoo ku sugnaa karantiil 14 maalmood ah Ranch Resort.
20-kii bishii Maarso, Mareykanka ayaa bilaabay inuu ciidamadiisa ka saaro Ciraaq si qayb ah sababo la xiriira cudurka faafa.
5-tii Febraayo, Wasaaradda Arrimaha Dibadda Shiinaha ayaa ku dhawaaqday in 21 dal (oo ay ku jiraan Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad iyo Tobago, Masar iyo Iiraan) ay caawimaad u dirtay Shiinaha.
Qaar ka mid ah ardayda Shiinaha ee ku jira jaamacadaha Mareykanka ayaa isugu yimid si ay u soo ururiyaan una diraan gargaarka gobollada Shiinaha ee ay ku dhaceen fayraska, iyadoo koox Chicago ah ay la sheegay inay bishii Janaayo 30 u dirtay 50 kun oo neefsashada N95 ah ee caafimaad ee gobolka Xubey.
Febraayo 5, Bill iyo Melinda Gates waxay ku dhawaaqeen inay ugu deeqeen 100 milyan oo doolarka Mareykanka ah WHO si ay u maalgeliyaan horumarinta tallaalka iyo daaweynta coronavirus, iyo sidoo kale si loo ilaaliyo dadka ka jira Afrika iyo Koonfurta Aasiya khatarta ugu jirta khatarta fayraska.
Interaksyon ayaa sheegtay in 6-dii Febraayo dowladda Shiinaha ay ugu deeqday Filibiin 200,000 oo maaskaro caafimaad kadib markii Senator Richard Gordon uu ugu diray Wuhan 3.16 milyan oo maaskaro ah.
