Tijaabada shaybaarka ee coronavirus-ka neefsashada 2019 (COVID-19) iyo fayraska SARS-CoV-2 ee la xiriira waxaa ka mid ah farsamooyinka lagu ogaanayo jiritaanka fayraska iyo farsamooyinka lagu ogaanayo jirka ka hortagga ee lagu soo saaro cudurka.
Qaabka loo aqoonsado fayraska waxaa xaqiijinaya in uu jiro OT-PCR, taas oo aqoonsaneysa RNA-ga coronavirus.
Tijaabadan ayaa gaar ah waxaana loogu talagalay in lagu ogaado RNA-ga fayraska SARS-CoV-2.
Waxaa loo isticmaalaa in lagu xaqiijiyo cudurro dhawaan ama firfircoon.
Soo-saarka antibody (serology) waxaa loo isticmaali karaa labadaba baaritaanka iyo xakamaynta dadka.
Baadhitaannada antibody-ka waxay muujinayaan tirada dadka qaba cudurka, oo ay ku jiraan kuwa aan calaamadaha lahayn in la isbitaalo tago ama aan la helin.
Heerarka saxda ah ee dhimashada cudurka iyo heerarka difaaca guud ee cudurka ayaa lagu ogaan karaa natiijooyinka baaritaanka.
Bishii Maarso ee sannadkii 2020 ma jirin wax xog ah oo lagu kalsoonaan karo oo ku saabsan faafitaanka fayraska dadka sababtoo ah fursadaha baaritaanka ayaa la xaddiday.
Ilaa 23ka Maarso, wadanna ma aysan awoodin in ay tijaabiyaan in ka badan 3% dadka ay ku nool yihiin, macluumaadka tirada baaritaannada ee lagu sameeyay dalal kala duwan ayaa aad u khilaafsan.
Waxaa suuragal ah in kala duwanaanta macluumaadka ay saameyn weyn ku yeelato heerarka dhimashada ee la diiwaangeliyey, taas oo laga yaabo in laga xadgudbo dalalka qaarkood.
Tijaabada waxaa lagu sameyn karaa nidaamka isku dhafka ee waqtiga dhabta ah ee loo yaqaan 'real-time reverse transcription chain reaction' (rRT-PCR) oo lagu sameeyay baaritaano ku saabsan neefsashada, oo lagu sameeyay habab kala duwan, oo ay ku jiraan masaajid sanka ama muunad caleen.
Natiijooyinka waxaa lagu helaa saacado ilaa laba maalmood.
Tijaabada OTC-PCR ee lagu sameeyo qoorta lagu qaado waxay ansax tahay toddobaadka ugu horeeya ee cudurka.
Markii dambe, fayraska ayaa laga yaabaa inuu ka baxo qoorta, laakiin wuxuu sii kordhayaa sanbabada.
Bukaanka qaba cudurka oo lagu tijaabiyo toddobaadka labaad ee cudurka, waxaa kale oo laga yaabaa in lagu qaado waxyaabaha neefta hoose ee ku jira iyada oo loo marayo qalabka nuugista ama la isticmaalo alaabta la cuno (mocrot).
Mid ka mid ah tijaabooyinka ugu horeeya ee PCR waxaa lagu sameeyay xarunta Sharite ee magaalada Berlin bishii Janaayo 2020 iyadoo la adeegsanayo falcelin silsilad ah oo leh wareejinta dhabta ah ee waqtiga dhabta ah (rRT-PCR) waxayna aasaas u noqotay 250,000 oo nooc oo ay markii dambe qaybisay Ururka Caafimaadka Adduunka (WHO).
Bishii Janaayo 23, 2020 Boqortooyada Midowday ayaa sidoo kale sameysay tijaabadeeda. Bishii Janaayo 28, 2020, shirkadda Koonfurta Kuuriya ee Kogenebiotech waxay sameysay qalab lagu ogaado SARS-CoV-2 oo ku saleysan PCR heerka bukaanka (PowerChek Coronavirus).
Waxay muujineysaa gen E oo ah mid guud oo dhammaan beta-coronavirus ah, iyo gen RdRp oo gaar u ah SARS-CoV-2. Shirkadda BGI Group ee Shiinaha ayaa ka mid noqotay shirkadaha ugu horreeya ee ka helay oggolaanshaha Maamulka Dawooyinka Qaranka ee Shiinaha ee isticmaalka degdegga ah ee SARS-CoV-2 si loo ogaado PCR. Maraykanka Xarumaha Xakamaynta iyo Kahortagga Cudurrada (CDC) waxay ku siiyaan International Reagent Resource inay ku siiyaan guddi ay ku sameeyaan PCR-ga waqtiga dhabta ah (2019-Novel Coronavirus (2019-nCoV) Real-Time RT-PCR Diagnostic Panel) shaybaarada caafimaadka dadweynaha.
